--- Linked Issue #327: comma and bracket combined? ---
```
parse("foo[]=1,2,3&foo[]=4,5,6", {comma: true})
/*
expected { foo: [ [ 1, 2, 3 ], [4, 5, 6] ] }
received { foo: [ 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 ] }

*/
```

uncertain if this is intentional or not

